SIMPLE: express_rifle
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Express rifle
<hw>Ex*press" ri"fle</hw>. <def>A sporting rifle for use at short
ranges, employing a large charge of powder and a light (short) bullet,
giving a high initial velocity and consequently a flat trajectory. It is
usually of moderately large caliber.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Express train</ent>⟦br⟧
